<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id90a5a6ad-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s6008"><num value="6008">§ 6008.</num><heading> Existing claims not affected</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Except as provided in <ref href="/us/usc/t22/s6004/a">section 6004(a) of this title</ref>, nothing in this chapter affects the provisions of <ref href="/us/usc/t22/s2370/a/2">section 2370(a)(2) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id90a5a6ae-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/102/484/dA/tXVII/s1709">Pub. L. 102–484, div. A, title XVII, § 1709</ref>, <date date="1992-10-23">Oct. 23, 1992</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/106/2580">106 Stat. 2580</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
